    div
      h3 <ruby>燈<rt>&thinsp;ㄉㄥ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>火<rt>&thinsp;ㄏㄨㄛˇ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>搖<rt>&thinsp;丨ㄠˊ&thinsp;</rt></ruby><ruby>曳<rt>&thinsp;丨ˋ&thinsp;</rt></ruby>
      dl
        dd None
